268
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:19,240
Title!

269
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:22,320
Title! Everyone, okay?

270
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,360
Where’s Title?

271
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:27,160
