273
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:34,120
Oh my.

274
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,280
Or you…

275
00:19:39,520 --> 00:19:40,560
Or maybe…

276
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,720
