344
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:46,000
- Ms. Kam!
- Ms. Kam!

345
00:24:46,080 --> 00:24:47,120
Um…

346
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:50,440
Actually, I just remembered

347
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:53,800
