and divide the money.

413
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:25,760
Some for emergencies,

414
00:28:26,360 --> 00:28:28,080
some for the house,

415
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:30,680
some for the Laab restaurant,

416
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:34,520
