428
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:03,840
Whoa, this is my golden year!

429
00:29:05,080 --> 00:29:06,680
Ms. Kam came to see me!

430
00:29:07,280 --> 00:29:11,560
<i>Finally, the urgent mission to find Title,</i>
