close to Granny Cheuy’s age.

446
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:01,320
The kid is chubby, like Typhoon,

447
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:03,240
and the other woman
looks like Bung, right?

448
00:30:03,840 --> 00:30:07,400
