450
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:14,520
But they look so similar!

451
00:30:14,600 --> 00:30:16,360
No, they don’t.

452
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:19,200
- Come on.
- Never mind.

453
00:30:19,280 --> 00:30:22,000
